                "invention-title": [
                    "Self-adaptive power following fuel cell vehicle energy management method and device",
                    "一种自适应功率跟随的燃料电池车整车能量管理方法及装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of hybrid electric vehicle whole vehicle energy management, and particularly provides a self-adaptive power following fuel cell vehicle whole vehicle energy management method and device, and the method comprises the steps: calculating a fuel cell efficient operation interval; calculating the historical average power of the whole vehicle operation and generating an average power array; calculating a current demand power predicted value of the whole vehicle through the whole vehicle operation historical average power array; calculating a fuel cell operation power compensation value in combination with the efficient operation interval; and calculating the real-time operation power of the fuel cell according to the current demand power predicted value of the whole vehicle and the operation power compensation value of the fuel cell. The operation power of the fuel cell is kept in an efficient power interval of the power generation efficiency of the fuel cell, and the power generation efficiency of the fuel cell is ensured. The electric quantity of the whole vehicle power battery is stabilized near a target value, the electric quantity fluctuation is small, the charging and discharging times of the power battery are few, and the service life of the power battery is long. The fuel cell is stable in operation condition, low in hydrogen consumption and long in service life."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于混合动力汽车整车能量管理技术领域，具体提供一种自适应功率跟随的燃料电池车整车能量管理方法及装置，所述方法包括：计算燃料电池高效运行区间；计算整车运行历史平均功率并生成平均功率数组；通过整车运行历史平均功率数组计算整车当前需求功率预测值；结合高效运行区间计算燃料电池运行功率补偿值；根据整车当前需求功率预测值和燃料电池运行功率补偿值计算燃料电池的实时运行功率。将燃料电池的运行功率保持在燃料电池发电效率的高效功率区间，保证燃料电池的发电效率。整车动力电池电量稳定在目标值附近，电量波动小，动力电池充放电次数少，动力电池的使用寿命长。燃料电池运行工况稳定，燃料电池氢耗低，燃料电池使用寿命长。"
                }
            ]
